{"tid":1253720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 向英國投訴, 停止出口催淚彈去香港","createTime":"2019-06-23T17:14:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T14:43:44.000Z","uid":9440,"like":149,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8e79376b07d4cb3dd9ceb3fc1ddef6144c44cf","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"依家香港其中一個供應催淚彈俾香港嘅武器商係一間叫做Chemring Defence嘅英國公司。呢個消息係俾英國Independence報紙 confirm左。Source: <a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/hong-kong-protests-tear-gas-uk-police-rubber-bullets-chemring-china-a8955636.html%3famp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-tear-gas-uk-police-rubber-bullets-chemring-china-a8955636.html%253famp&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr146aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=39902bae\" target=\"_blank\">www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/hong-kong-protests-tear-gas-uk-police-rubber-bullets-chemring-china-a8955636.html%3famp</a><br />\n<br />\n呢一間武器商出口催淚彈去香港係需要一個由英國政府approve嘅牌照。而呢一個牌一但被approve 可以喺5年內無限量出口俾黑警。<br />\n<br />\n對上一次呢一個牌照係喺2015年approve, 即係喺2020年呢一個牌照係需要再俾review同approve。<br />\n<br />\n啲黑警掟150個催淚彈掟得咁爽, 如果個牌approve唔到咁佢地就可以共享大灣區榮譽同公安一齊愛國用國貨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多日外國媒體嘅報導再加上Amnesty International (source: <a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2019/06/hong-kong-police-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org%2Fen%2Flatest%2Fnews%2F2019%2F06%2Fhong-kong-police-violence%2F&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr146aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=798df35f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2019/06/hong-kong-police-violence/</a>) 嘅調查結果應該基於人道理由有足夠嘅理據去俾英國重新審視呢個牌照。<br />\n<br />\n問題係依家應該要向英國邊一個部門投訴, 係independence 篇報導係有講過個 Department for International Trade, 上網search係搵到有一個department 係特別係關於香港嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/world/organisations/department-for-international-trade-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fworld%2Forganisations%2Fdepartment-for-international-trade-hong-kong&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr146aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=d55e5198\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/world/organisations/department-for-international-trade-hong-kong</a>我地可以係呢一到出發先。<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲係呢一方面有d認識?"},{"pid":"d4d0533278f03c0edf7fd1c5a33d4cf94981d7b8","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:14:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0343749bc17ba9532900e0f2b72a3b777bd18a4","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7ccabc2287e2f4a6e30aca2cb2b6f64fd7287635","tid":1253720,"uid":244243,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"785ad7d52aefc69d55f97ea2c5f5c743ed716997","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"推到大家見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c6928081ad081d04831d5aaf259e5bfe6e2ac7","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"838e13a6b87112ae8255f6882effa12d19811c17","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9c247124a800e8c9e1fb525f348d53e4fc609435","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"愛國用國貨"},{"pid":"693fd8b778e5ece00aec8c10f80a8c651a1ced81","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201