uote":{"pid":"9c247124a800e8c9e1fb525f348d53e4fc609435","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"愛國用國貨"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"會唔會變毒氣彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a542016547ffc93189536be9b16138556282f27","tid":1253720,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97700e64017e0852ed46640aac9985a598e114de","tid":1253720,"uid":115539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88251454d0d156f0c8fc640a1f1667b73e2db839","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"要搞到佢地無野掟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:20:40.000Z","msg":"有內地貨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d217a4e07dd888970802546167d0631b7ae8635","tid":1253720,"uid":208253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"Sorry 㩒錯咗負皮...<br />\n推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1e6dee6be3aeaf63177d5024040c1ecb6e5e24","tid":1253720,"uid":32204,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:22:23.000Z","msg":"之前有 MP 問咗 Mark Field 咁答:<br />\nThe right hon. Gentleman touched on the use of tear gas and rubber bullets, and I would therefore like to talk a bit about export licences; I know this has been brought up in the pages of The Guardian today. The last export licence from the UK for tear gas hand grenades and tear gas cartridges used for training purposes by the Hong Kong police was in July 2018. The last export licence for rubber bullets was in July 2015. We rejected an open licence for riot shields as recently as April 2019. The issue of export licences is close to all our hearts, and it comes up time and again in our work overseas. We are monitoring the situation very closely and will of course undertake to review all current export licences. We will have no qualms in revoking any licences found no longer to be consistent with the consolidated criteria, ​including criterion 2, which I think the right hon. Gentleman will be aware of, dealing with respect for human rights.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6490adbd1f1d3bf4e0f933f4137ff83ee5c9478f","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"再補充之前有巴打話停止佢地用加拿大防毒面具面具, 其實個d唔係一d law enforcement 嘅工具, 無咩特別嘅出口限制應該容易係第二間買, 停左佢地催淚彈先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4f5001ad6b90141495c6a46ea90214411129d1","tid":1253720,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:22:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n[整合]點擊這裏了解黎緊一星期香港人行程<br />\n<a