E0A10A0/HongKong</a><br />\n<br />\n係議會上嘅對答"},{"pid":"1829d900f4fddf01f11097797fb3a25a2b32abce","tid":1253720,"uid":112706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"House of Commons入面係Committee on Arms Export Controls<br />\n同時因為係Foreign Affairs, 所以都關 Foreign Affairs Commitee 事。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76d76b6558f88229a38187028d39615246c9b71","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1829d900f4fddf01f11097797fb3a25a2b32abce","tid":1253720,"uid":112706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"House of Commons入面係Committee on Arms Export Controls<br />\n同時因為係Foreign Affairs, 所以都關 Foreign Affairs Commitee 事。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa4c2b6b420073ad7bc9ad6d5326ab752c3cd15","tid":1253720,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbecaf0ff07c4234a3a20231ebadb989f986cd8a","tid":1253720,"uid":33668,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"唔好呀<br />\n<br />\n英國唔出口 supplier 換大陸制 到時真係會死人駕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"自己擺喺倉都爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c1adbd2758549fb5c1cc19c4c25cad8c645e27","tid":1253720,"uid":112706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d76d76b6558f88229a38187028d39615246c9b71","tid":1253720,"uid":9440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1829d900f4fddf01f11097797fb3a25a2b32abce","tid":1253720,"uid":112706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T17:28:10.000Z","msg":"House of Commons入面係Committee on Arms Export Controls<br />\n同